{"type":null,"faqId":49701,"title":"如何调整备忘录的字体大小？","answer":"<div id=\"body8709019\">\n<p class=\"notestext\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264507__p49906328\">\n<p class=\"notestext\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264507__p5502427155235\">暂没有专门针对备忘录字体进行单独调整的设置项。</p>\n<p class=\"notestext\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264507__p49906328\">可以通过调节系统字体大小来进行调节。请进入<span class=\"menucascade\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264507__menucascade15822771154711\">“<span class=\"uicontrol\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264507__uicontrol49916086154711\">设置</span> &gt; <span class=\"uicontrol\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264507__uicontrol46591594154711\">显示</span> &gt; <span class=\"uicontrol\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264507__uicontrol16671166154711\">文字大小</span>”</span>，选择合适的字体。设置完毕后包括信息、联系人等字体大小均会同步调整。</p>\n<p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264507__p4386525316205\"><span><a class=\"thickbox\" href=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/93f4f_fjcxk.png\"><img id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264507__image15118044162013\" src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/93f4f_fjcxk.png\"></a></span></p>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"familylinks\"></div>\n</div>","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022264507","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448590015000,"seriesProductName":"NXT-AL10A,NXT-AL10B,NXT-AL10C,NXT-CL00A,NXT-DL00A,NXT-TL00A","visitedTimes":22,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"调整,备忘录,字体","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}